race.description: The Prince Of Merewether Midway Handicap
race.comment: LISTINS LASS (8) appreciated the drop in class when an eye-catching second over this distance at Tuncurry last time out. Draws a far better alley and although up grade drops a whopping 10kgs after the claim. Should be powering home again. CUBAN CIGAR (9) did his best work late and wasn't beaten far when fresh from a spell over 1100m at Wyong recently. A wide gate doesn't help but an extra 100m does so this sparingly raced three-year-old gets his chance. FUN SPONGE (11) might get a soft run up near the lead and if so can make amends for a poor effort here 20 days ago. COSY CORNER (5) should be right at her peak fourth up and appears the next in line.
